# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# HindiAudiobook.com — Environment Variables
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
# SETUP INSTRUCTIONS:
# 1. Is file ko copy karein: cp .env.local.example .env.local
# 2. Apna password set karein neeche
# 3. Vercel par bhi yeh variables add karein:
#    Vercel Dashboard → Project → Settings → Environment Variables
#

# ── Google AdSense ────────────────────────────────────────────
# Aapka AdSense Publisher ID
# Google AdSense → Account → Account information → Publisher ID
# Format: ca-pub-XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX
NEXT_PUBLIC_ADSENSE_CLIENT=ca-pub-XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX

# ── Admin Password ────────────────────────────────────────────
# Yeh password /admin/login par maanga jaayega
# STRONG password rakhen — kam se kam 12 characters
# Example: MyAdmin@2024!Secure
ADMIN_PASSWORD=apna_strong_password_yahan_likhein

# ── Session Secret ────────────────────────────────────────────
# Ek random string jo session cookie ko secure banata hai
# Koi bhi random string likhen — jitna lamba utna acha
# Example: xK9$mN2pL7@qR4sT8vW1yZ6
SESSION_SECRET=apna_random_secret_yahan_likhein

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# VERCEL PAR KAISE SET KAREIN:
# 1. vercel.com → apna project kholein
# 2. Settings → Environment Variables
# 3. Add karein:
#    Name: ADMIN_PASSWORD    Value: [aapka password]
#    Name: SESSION_SECRET    Value: [random string]
# 4. Production + Preview + Development sab select karein
# 5. Save → Redeploy
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
